          The magic happens when game events occur at fan-owned locations. Goals, saves, corners, or other significant plays—depending on the sport—automatically trigger point rewards through the platform.
        </p>
        <p>
          This point system creates continuous engagement throughout every match. Fans actively monitor their sections, tracking the flow of play and celebrating each time the action moves into their territory.
        </p>
        <p>
